Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.78,0:01:47.49,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我是不是墜入愛河了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.53,0:01:50.11,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}24小時滿腦子都是你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}意識不受控制
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:54.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}覺得與平時不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:53.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}覺\N得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.73,0:01:57.24,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和你生硬的對話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.27,0:01:56.25,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}兩\N個\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:02:00.09,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}難道  不對  是單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:01:58.97,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}兩\N情\N相\N悅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.13,0:02:02.46,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟了  視線和他對上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:06.61,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}什麼什麼  這種忐忑心情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.76,0:02:12.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思考回路亂成一團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:18.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那種事情  我可是第一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:22.43,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感覺都要發燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:26.63,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}急轉直下的我的愛慕之情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.30,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眨眼間  臉像著火般變得通紅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:31.87,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}怎怎怎麼可能  我的手居然在顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.70,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這是所謂的戀愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:37.20,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不不不不好了  說話咬到舌頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.95,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}糟糕的沉默  我語無倫次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.99,0:02:42.58,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想知道  你對我的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:41.17,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\an6}你\N對\N我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.63,0:02:45.15,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}單單單單☆單相思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.39,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}初戀！  在平日的上學路上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:51.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}閃閃發光  I DO fall in love！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:54.41,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}好像能在天空飛翔般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:57.53,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}單單單單☆單相思
